This is a warning and a rescue plan. You need to do this message. There is only destruction at the end of the road unless you follow Christ.

He is your only hope. You must believe. You have a world full of people doing their thing. At the end of that is destruction. Following Christ has consequences. Leaving you here for the bearers of this message. Understand what it means to follow Jesus.